info.instr: At third floor, head straight and go through door  OR  take stairs to the right
Enter through the single brown door at the bottom of the stairway
Turn right and walk to the end of the hall
Enter the doorway and turn (Note: elevators on left and stairs on right)
Once exit the elevator turn right, pass the pulmonary allergy critical care and sleep medicine center, and then turn left  OR  Exit the stairwell and head straight
Enter the door at the end of the hall
You are now on the 3rd floor of Dwan Cardio
